---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: The Ministry of Endorsement
description: Essays, reflections, and documents related to endorsement ministry
---

<div class="endorsement-page">

  <p class="essay-back"><a href="/">← Back to Home</a></p>

  <div class="endorsement-layout">

    <aside class="endorsement-nav">
      <h1>The Ministry of<br>Endorsement</h1>

      <p class="endorsement-subtitle">
        Exploring endorsement ministry—its role, its structure, and its place within The United Methodist Church
      </p>

      <div class="endorsement-nav-group">
        <button class="endorsement-nav-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          Framing Reflections
        </button>
        <div class="endorsement-nav-menu">
          <ul class="link-list">
            {% for item in collections.endorsementItems %}
              {% if item.data.form == "reflection" %}
                <li><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></li>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="endorsement-nav-group">
        <button class="endorsement-nav-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          Interpretive Essays
        </button>
        <div class="endorsement-nav-menu">
          <ul class="link-list">
            {% for item in collections.endorsementItems %}
              {% if item.data.form == "essay" %}
                <li><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></li>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="endorsement-nav-group">
        <button class="endorsement-nav-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          Foundational Documents
        </button>
        <div class="endorsement-nav-menu endorsement-nav-menu--foundational">

          <p class="foundation-menu-note">
            If you are new to this material, the White Paper provides the fullest introduction.
            Executive Summaries and Briefs offer shorter pathways into the same work.
          </p>

          <ul class="link-list series-link-list">

            {% for item in collections.endorsementItems | sort(attribute="data.series_title") %}
              {% if item.data.level == "foundational" and item.data.series_slug and item.data.series_order == 1 %}

                <li class="series-group-title">
                  <a href="/series/{{ item.data.series_slug }}/">{{ item.data.series_title }} Series</a>
                </li>

                {% for seriesItem in collections.endorsementItems | sort(attribute="data.series_order") %}
                  {% if seriesItem.data.level == "foundational" and seriesItem.data.series_slug == item.data.series_slug %}
                    <li class="series-group-item">
                      <a href="{{ seriesItem.url }}">
                        Part {{ seriesItem.data.series_order }}: {{ seriesItem.data.title }}
                      </a>
                    </li>
                  {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}

              {% elif item.data.level == "foundational" and not item.data.series_slug %}
                <li><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></li>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}

          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="endorsement-main">

      <section class="endorsement-feature">
        <article class="endorsement-feature-card">
          <h2>Featured Works</h2>

          {% for item in collections.endorsementItems | sort(attribute="data.feature_section_order") %}
            {% if item.data.feature_section == "endorsement" %}

              <div class="endorsement-feature-item">

                <h3>
                  <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
                </h3>

                {% if item.data.subtitle %}
                  <p class="endorsement-feature-subtitle">
                    {{ item.data.subtitle }}
                  </p>
                {% endif %}

                {% if item.data.feature_blurb or item.data.feature_excerpt %}
                  <div class="endorsement-feature-excerpt">
                    <p>{{ item.data.feature_blurb or item.data.feature_excerpt }}</p>
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

              </div>

            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}

        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="endorsement-howto panel">
        <h2>How to Use This Section</h2>
        <p>
          This section is arranged as a working shelf rather than a chronological feed.
          Some items are formal documents in PDF form. Others are essays or reflections
          meant to frame the questions, stakes, and vocabulary of endorsement ministry.
        </p>
        <p>
          Readers new to the subject may wish to begin with the framing reflection and
          then move into the foundational papers. Those already familiar with the field
          may prefer to enter directly through the documents most relevant to their
          interests.
        </p>
      </section>

    </main>

  </div>
</div>

{% include "partials/shelf-script.njk" %}